eas_text: A civil authority has issued A FIRE WARNING for the following counties or areas: Laramie, WY; at 05:06 PM ON DEC 17, 2025 Effective until 01:06 AM DEC 18, 2025. Message from WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: Wild Fire in Winchester HIlls Due to a large grass fire threatening structures in the Winchester Hills area all residents need to evacuate immediately.  Local Law Enforcement and Fire will direct residents where to go.  Standby for location on evacuation shelter.
